SELECT
  (
    SELECT
      AVG(T1.Consumption)
    FROM YearMonth AS T1
    INNER JOIN Customers AS T2
      ON T1.CustomerID = T2.CustomerID
    WHERE
      SUBSTR(T1.Date, 1, 4) = '2013'
      AND T2.Currency = 'CZK'
    GROUP BY
      T2.Segment
    HAVING
      T2.Segment = 'SME'
  ) - (
    SELECT
      AVG(T1.Consumption)
    FROM YearMonth AS T1
    INNER JOIN Customers AS T2
      ON T1.CustomerID = T2.CustomerID
    WHERE
      SUBSTR(T1.Date, 1, 4) = '2013'
      AND T2.Currency = 'CZK'
    GROUP BY
      T2.Segment
    HAVING
      T2.Segment = 'LAM'
  ) AS SME_LAM_Difference,
  (
    SELECT
      AVG(T1.Consumption)
    FROM YearMonth AS T1
    INNER JOIN Customers AS T2
      ON T1.CustomerID = T2.CustomerID
    WHERE
      SUBSTR(T1.Date, 1, 4) = '2013'
      AND T2.Currency = 'CZK'
    GROUP BY
      T2.Segment
    HAVING
      T2.Segment = 'LAM'
  ) - (
    SELECT
      AVG(T1.Consumption)
    FROM YearMonth AS T1
    INNER JOIN Customers AS T2
      ON T1.CustomerID = T2.CustomerID
    WHERE
      SUBSTR(T1.Date, 1, 4) = '2013'
      AND T2.Currency = 'CZK'
    GROUP BY
      T2.Segment
    HAVING
      T2.Segment = 'KAM'
  ) AS LAM_KAM_Difference,
  (
    SELECT
      AVG(T1.Consumption)
    FROM YearMonth AS T1
    INNER JOIN Customers AS T2
      ON T1.CustomerID = T2.CustomerID
    WHERE
      SUBSTR(T1.Date, 1, 4) = '2013'
      AND T2.Currency = 'CZK'
    GROUP BY
      T2.Segment
    HAVING
      T2.Segment = 'KAM'
  ) - (
    SELECT
      AVG(T1.Consumption)
    FROM YearMonth AS T1
    INNER JOIN Customers AS T2
      ON T1.CustomerID = T2.CustomerID
    WHERE
      SUBSTR(T1.Date, 1, 4) = '2013'
      AND T2.Currency = 'CZK'
    GROUP BY
      T2.Segment
    HAVING
      T2.Segment = 'SME'
  ) AS KAM_SME_Difference;	----- bird -----	debit_card_specializing

SELECT
  Segment,
  PercentageIncrease
FROM (
  SELECT
    c.Segment,
    (
      (
        SUM(CASE WHEN SUBSTR(ym.Date, 1, 4) = '2013' THEN ym.Consumption ELSE 0 END) - SUM(CASE WHEN SUBSTR(ym.Date, 1, 4) = '2012' THEN ym.Consumption ELSE 0 END)
      ) * 100.0 / SUM(CASE WHEN SUBSTR(ym.Date, 1, 4) = '2012' THEN ym.Consumption ELSE 0 END)
    ) AS PercentageIncrease,
    RANK() OVER (ORDER BY (
      (
        SUM(CASE WHEN SUBSTR(ym.Date, 1, 4) = '2013' THEN ym.Consumption ELSE 0 END) - SUM(CASE WHEN SUBSTR(ym.Date, 1, 4) = '2012' THEN ym.Consumption ELSE 0 END)
      ) * 100.0 / SUM(CASE WHEN SUBSTR(ym.Date, 1, 4) = '2012' THEN ym.Consumption ELSE 0 END)
    ) DESC) AS RankAsc,
    RANK() OVER (ORDER BY (
      (
        SUM(CASE WHEN SUBSTR(ym.Date, 1, 4) = '2013' THEN ym.Consumption ELSE 0 END) - SUM(CASE WHEN SUBSTR(ym.Date, 1, 4) = '2012' THEN ym.Consumption ELSE 0 END)
      ) * 100.0 / SUM(CASE WHEN SUBSTR(ym.Date, 1, 4) = '2012' THEN ym.Consumption ELSE 0 END)
    ) ASC) AS RankDesc
  FROM yearmonth AS ym
  JOIN customers AS c
    ON ym.CustomerID = c.CustomerID
  WHERE
    c.Currency = 'EUR' AND SUBSTR(ym.Date, 1, 4) IN ('2012', '2013')
  GROUP BY
    c.Segment
)
WHERE
  RankAsc = 1 OR RankDesc = 1;	----- bird -----	debit_card_specializing

SELECT
  CASE
    WHEN (
      SELECT
        COUNT(CASE WHEN SEX = 'M' AND Admission = '+' THEN ID ELSE NULL END)
      FROM Patient
    ) > (
      SELECT
        COUNT(CASE WHEN SEX = 'M' AND Admission = '-' THEN ID ELSE NULL END)
      FROM Patient
    )
    THEN 'More in-patients'
    WHEN (
      SELECT
        COUNT(CASE WHEN SEX = 'M' AND Admission = '+' THEN ID ELSE NULL END)
      FROM Patient
    ) < (
      SELECT
        COUNT(CASE WHEN SEX = 'M' AND Admission = '-' THEN ID ELSE NULL END)
      FROM Patient
    )
